Very good list.  I find it delightful that many others agree with the proposition that Asaya's Insight should be useable on others.  It would fit so well with the class theme.  <br />
<br />
I also agree that, if more dds are added, they should be innovative and not redundant.  Emilia's <br />
suggestion of &quot;fast brutal expensive spells&quot; would help fill this niche as would an arcane/ice type char that would be similar to the char itself yet have sufficiently different characteristics such as focusing more on the subsequent damage.  <br />
<br />
The class has enough wards and enough crowd control.  What is needed are some tweaks to the damage options and refinement of the anti-magic defense ability and to become more unique.  Self-only junk hopefully is not being contemplated in place of substantive ideas.</div>
