<br />
Seradon : 2172dmg 414 Energy 4.0 Second  25% Root<br />
New Seradon : 2672 dmg 374 Energy 3.0 Seconds <br />
(35% haste needed, so you are forced to have 5% worn haste minimum)<br />
<br />
Flamespear : 2351+508dmg 499energy 4Second  36Range<br />
New Flamespear : 3600+750 499Energy 4Second Channeled   10Sec Refresh<br />
(you need 50% spell haste for best results)<br />
