</div>
<br />
This is incorrect. Special Attacks are considered whatever they are flagged as. Melee specials costing endurance are flagged as melee attacks and do work when silenced.<br />
<br />
Some classes like the Shaman have specials that cost endurance and are flagged as spells, but those are the exception, and they usually cost energy <b>and </b>endurance.</div>
